platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: If you want to play fantasy sports, there are—ahem—leagues of apps to choose from. But we think ESPN Fantasy might be the MVP. Its minimal interface stays out of our way so we can focus on draft picks, trades, and managing our lineup. But the best part? ESPN’s got mini-stories on all of the hot prospects. So the more time we spend actually using the app, the better our team ends up.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Create a fantasy team with friends and get the most out of game day.
